criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Individuals diagnosed with breast cancer in adjuvant and neoadjuvant radiotherapy
             treatment;

          -  Both female and male participants are being studiedolder;

          -  Minimum age of participants is 18 years.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Not being with consciousness, memory and orientation preserved;

          -  Patients with clinical conditions that affect the continuity in the study or express
             request not to continue participating in the study.
